1 a. A detailed report on funds expended for the program for the 2026-2027
2 fiscal year.
3 b. An assessment of the effectiveness of programs funded by grants
4 awarded under this section in improving maternal health outcomes for
5 black women.
6 c. Recommendations for future grant programs to be administered by the
7 Department and for future funding opportunities for community-based
8 organizations to improve maternal health outcomes for black women
9 through programs and resources that are aligned with evidence-based
10 practices for improving maternal health outcomes for black women.
